ckground:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Diaz\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[Rey Gallegos]]\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! En-Joo\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[Tim Kang]]\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Father Arthur Marsh\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[Ken Howard]]\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Major Pa Tee Tint\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| Maung Maung Khin\n| {{N/A|Maung Maung Khin<br />''(archival footage)''}}\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Lieutenant Aye\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| Aung Aay Noi\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|- \n! Gabriela\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[Yvette Monreal]]\n| style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Maria Beltran \n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[Adriana Barraza]]\n| style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Carmen Delgado\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[Paz Vega]]\n| style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Hugo Martinez\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[Sergio Peris-Mencheta]]\n| style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Victor Martinez\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[\u00d3scar Jaenada]]\n| style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|}\n\n===Crew===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center; width:99%;\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Film\n! colspan=\"7\"|Crew/Detail\n|-\n! Composer(s)\n! Cinematographer\n! Editor(s)\n! Production <br />Companies\n! Distributing <br />Company\n! Running time\n|-\n! ''[[First Blood]]''\n| rowspan=\"3\"| [[Jerry Goldsmith]]\n| [[Andrew Laszlo]]\n| Joan E. Chapman\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Anabasis Investments, N. V.\n| [[Orion Pictures]]\n| 93 minutes\n|-\n! ''[[Rambo: First Blood Part II|Rambo: <br /> First Blood Part II]]''\n| [[Jack Cardiff]]\n| [[Mark Goldblatt]] and [[Mark Helfrich (film editor)|Mark Helfrich]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[TriStar Pictures]]\n| 96 minutes\n|-\n! ''[[Rambo III]]''\n| John Stanier\n| James Symons, Andrew London and O. Nicholas Brown\n| [[Carolco Pictures]]\n| 101 minutes\n|-\n! ''[[Rambo (2008 film)|Rambo]]''\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Brian Tyler]]\n| [[Glen MacPherson]]\n| Sean Albertson\n| [[Nu Image]] <br />Equity Pictures Medienfonds GmbH and Co. KG IV\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Lionsgate Films|Lionsgate]]\n| 91 minutes<hr />{{small|Extended Cut:}} <br /> 99 minutes\n|-\n! ''[[Rambo: Last Blood|Rambo: <br /> Last Blood]]''\n| Brendan Galvin\n| Todd E. Miller and Carsten Kurpanek \n| Millennium Media <br />[[Balboa Productions]] <br />Templeton Media\n| 89 minutes<hr />{{small|International:}} <br /> 101 minutes\n|}\n\n==Reception==\n===Box office performance===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Film\n! rowspan=\"2\" | U.S. release date\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Budget \n! colspan=\"3\" | Box office revenue \n|-\n! style=\"text-align:center;\"| United States\n! style=\"text-align:center;\"| International\n! style=\"text-align:center;\"| Worldwide \n|-\n| ''[[First Blood]]''<ref>{{cite web | url= http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=firstblood.htm | title = First Blood (1982) | work = [[Box Office Mojo]] }}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | October 22, 1982\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $15 million\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $47,212,904\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $78,000,000\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $125,212,904\n|-\n| ''[[Rambo: First Blood Part II]]''<ref>{{cite web | url= http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=rambo2.htm | title = Rambo: First Blood Part II (1985) | work = [[Box Office Mojo]] }}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | May 22, 1985\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $25 million\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $150,415,432\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $149,985,000\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $300,400,432\n|-\n| ''[[Rambo III]]''<ref>{{cite web | url= http://boxofficemojo.com