i T. Podovsky\n| style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[Steven Berkoff]]\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Sergeant Yushin\n| style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| Voyo Goric\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Lieutenant Tay\n| style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[George Cheung]]\n| style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| {{N/A|George Cheung<br />''(archival footage)''}}\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Captain Vinh\n| style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| William Ghent \n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Robert Griggs\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[Kurtwood Smith]]\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Mousa Ghani\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[Sasson Gabai]]\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Masoud\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[Spiros Foc\u00e1s]]\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Hamid\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| Doudi Shoua\n| {{N/A|Doudi Shoua<br />''(archival footage)''}}\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Colonel Alexei Zaysen\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[Marc de Jonge]]\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Sergeant Kourov\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| Randy Raney\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Sarah Miller\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[Julie Benz]]\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Michael Burnett\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[Paul Schulze]]\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! School Boy\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[Matthew Marsden]]\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n|-\n! Lewis\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" |\n| [[Graham McTavish]]\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\